title: Week 11 Preview; Another Lock off?
itunes:title: Week 11 Preview; Another Lock off?
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal & Chris Wesseling take a look at all of the Week 11 action, starting with a recap of Thursday night’s Steelers- Titans matchup (1:00), Dan envisions Sessler’s solo man trip to Cancun before coming back down to reality to preview games starting with the Bears (9;12) What the fork is happening in this 2017 NFL season? (29;29). Some breaking news in Mexico and Dan tries to get Tamposi fired up about the Patriots, but her immune system took a hit, so no luck. (1;00;08) Another lock off happens (1:10;08) plus much more!
